thread.title: Giovanni Angioni

author: Giovanni Angioni
title: Giovanni Angioni
text:
MissHosting support service is probably the worst one I ever tried: unresponsive, unhelpful, and populated by operators who's only answer seems to be "Buy another plan!" - although I have already a whole VPS, not a s***y shared hosting.
However, for the first time, Pratik was able to help me and to fix some issues with their server in no time. FANTASTIC SERVICE!
